                        <strong> Introduction to HR Management</strong>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                    data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">

                        HR technology, also known as Human Resources Technology or HR Tech, refers to the
                        application of technology solutions and software tools to streamline and automate HR
                        processes and tasks within an organization. It encompasses a wide range of software
                        applications, platforms, and systems designed to enhance HR functions and improve overall HR
                        management.
                    </div>
                </div>
